5:
Thanks for the invitation, Mister!
Everything looks delicious!
8:
No need to thank me. This is merely
what friends do for each other, no?
10:
As a matter of fact, I've procured an
especially fine delicacy for you
today...
14:
Oh... OH! Is this that fancy caviar
stuff? Wow! How'd you afford so
much of it?!
25:
You must be worn out. I'll have a bed
prepared in one of my extra rooms,
so you may take a rest there if you'd
like.
33:
Looks like that little concoction
worked perfectly... Alchemy is a
wonderful thing.
38:
H-huh? Mister?! Why... Ouch!
Hey! What's going on here?
40:
My apologies, my dear. I'm afraid I
had to restrain you.
42:
There's no escape. You'll be mine
forever, now.
45:
N-no way! I'm a servant of the
people, not your toy! You need to let
me go!
48:
My, so feisty. I'll need you to calm
down in your new room.
52:
Ouch... They really don't know how to
treat a lady.
55:
*whimper*
How could he trap us here like this...
57:
How long is he going to keep us
locked up for? I wanna go home!
60:
Yikes, looks like we're dealing with a
major league creep.
63:
Don't worry, girls. Everything's gonna
be okay now!
66:
She's never further than a hop, skip,
and a jump away...
70:
Able to leap over the ocean in a
single bound! Never fear, the Marine
Bunny Princess Faroa is here!
73:
Help's going to arrive any moment,
now. Let's just be patient for a little
longer...
81:
You're going to allow yourself to get
kidnapped?!
85:
We'll attack from within and without!
It'll be the fastest way to take this
creep down!
94:
Not alone, no. That's why I need your
help!
96:
I'd probably only manage to save a
few people before getting caught if I
went on my own.
100:
But with you guys, we'll be able to
save everyone in one fell swoop!
105:
...We cannot refuse such a noble
endeavor.
110: Don't worry, we've got your back.
113:
W-we're going to run? But that man
has so many guards...
116:
Taking care of the nasty old man will
be a cinch for me.
118:
We can't let people like that get
away with what they're doing!
127: Not at all. You're just on time!
133:
Now, then. Let's get ourselves some
payback!
136: S-sir! The girls... they've all escaped!
151: As if I'm gonna let you get away!
158:
Don't worry, I hit him with the blunt
end.
166:
I'm glad everything worked out in
the end.
173:
Thank you, Faroa! H-how can we
ever repay you?
179:
No matter how dark the skies may
seem, Faroa will be there in your
time of need!
